Da Brat https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Da_Brat 0 Shawntae Harris (born April 14, 1974), better known by her stage name Da Brat, is an American rapper and actress from Chicago. Beginning her career in 1992, her debut album Funkdafied (1994) sold one million copies, making her the first female solo rap act to receive a platinum certification, and the second overall female rap act (solo or group) after Salt-N-Pepa. Brat has received two Grammy Award nominations. Shawntae_Harris ( born April_14_,_1974 ) , better_known by her_stage_name_Da_Brat , is an_American_rapper_and_actress from Chicago .
